<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Leave Balance Awarded</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; background-color:
      #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; } .container { width: 80%; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: #ffffff; } .header { text-align: center; padding-bottom:
      20px; } .content { margin-top: 20px; } .footer { margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center; font-size: 0.9em; color: #777; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Leave Balance Awarded</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        <p>We are pleased to inform you that a leave balance has been awarded to
          you. Below are the details:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Leave Type:</strong> {{leaveType}}</li>
          <li><strong>Leave Balance:</strong> {{leaveBalance}} days</li>
        </ul>
        {{! <p>Please make sure to utilize your leave balance within the stipulated
          time frame.</p> }}
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact the HR department.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>{{companyName}}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>